Cell["\<\
(#2.1.3.1): Solving for the Boundaries using Kerner\[CloseCurlyQuote]s \
Hamiltonian:\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.990743376196884*^9, 
  3.9907433902702713`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"17696c19-db1c-4070-87ae-\
