Cell["\<\
Can we see if this is the number that appears on the plot earlier:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.988473784774229*^9, 
  3.988473791540259*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"651b1532-dcdf-4149-be51-\
2afed1b1e609"],

