Cell["\<\
Let\[CloseCurlyQuote]s find the low-temperature behavior by expanding E(T) \
about T = 0.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9884493509823027`*^9, 3.9884493703674593`*^9}, 
