Cell["\<\
Oh, nuts. There is some parameter thing going on here... Seems like the \
heat-capacity may become imaginary if \[Gamma] in relation to T is not nice...\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9884742183028708`*^9, 
  3.988474242790901*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"5545e764-6c44-4050-b339-\
4ce5716d2cdd"],

