51f61bd951f0"],

Cell["\<\
First of all, it is astounding that the dependence on \[Beta] and \[Delta] \
just goes away in this derivative... Obviously, it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s just \
math, but it is nonetheless wildly unexpected.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.990310631356532*^9, 
  3.990310673556365*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"93df1c82-6868-4e7d-b11d-\
